;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501031201: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P20135/NPCAct/Act501031201.json-->
::'''Thea:''' Hey, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}}! Are you experiencing issues with your phone such as lagging, overheating, or system-based stoppages? I can help you upgrade your system.
::'''Thea:''' For just a tiny amount of credits, your phone will gain a new lease on life and its operating system will function smoother than the Star Rail that lines the cosmos...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501031201_10-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501031201_10-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What kind of upgrade are we talking about?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031204-->
:::'''Thea:''' Ahem, it's actually about an exclusive piece of technology from my company, and I'm the only person on this planet who can access it.
:::'''Thea:''' I can't reveal too much about it since it's exclusive.
:::'''Thea:''' Anyway, give it a try and see for yourself. And don't worry. I won't charge you if you're not satisfied.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Pretend to be clueless) Star Rail?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031208-->
:::'''Thea:''' It's the track on which the Astral Express runs. You must have heard of them, right? Those elusive star-seeking travelers...
:::'''Thea:''' Rumor has it that they were the ones who brought "portable communicators" &mdash; known to us as phones &mdash; to this planet. But apparently, they don't care about customer service at all. How irresponsible!
:::'''Thea:''' That's why we of the IPC are here to clean up their mess!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501031201_20-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501031201_20-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Please help me upgrade my phone.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031212-->
::::'''Thea:''' No problem. I've already helped over two dozen customers.
::::'''Thea:''' Next, I'll access data from the other side of the galaxy and transfer it straight from the IPC's headquarters into your device.
::::'''Thea:''' (Pretending to work hard) Hmmm... Hyaa... Hah! Look, it's done.
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} And then what?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031216-->
::::'''Thea:''' And then voilà! Now, enjoy its ultra-smooth operating system!
::::'''Thea:''' Just check it out! Look at its interface and these animations, and experience this perfectly designed haptic pressure sensors and tap-feedback system...
::::'''Thea:''' ...Ahem, sorry, I used to work in the user experience department, so I'm a bit obsessed with these details...
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Well, I'm from the Astral Express.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031220-->
::::'''Thea:''' Wait, you? This... I mean... You know...
::::'''Thea:''' I didn't mean to badmouth you! I'm just... you know... just trying to provide more reliable warranty services for the locals!
::::'''Thea:''' These folks take forever to even unlock their phones. Without professional guidance like mine, they'd fall prey to all sorts of sneaky auto-pay services...
::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501031202: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P20135/NPCAct/Act501031202.json-->
::'''Thea:''' Hey there, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mister}}. If you ever have any questions about phones, feel free to drop by anytime.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
:{{DIcon}} Can we talk...?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501031203: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P20135/NPCAct/Act501031203.json-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501031251-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031251-->
:;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 414010901-->)
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Are you sticking around here?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031246-->
::::'''Thea:''' Well, someone has to teach the locals how to use these phones. I've already done my best to keep the charges as low as possible.
::::'''Thea:''' Thanks to me, the miners here are getting the hang of it. Isn't that a good thing?
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How did you solve the issues with the phones?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031252-->
::::'''Thea:''' Well... Fine, I can tell you, but this is just between us, alright?
::::'''Thea:''' As you know, all the major operating systems are developed and maintained by the IPC...
::::'''Thea:''' To save computing power, the IPC has marked devices as "discarded" if their system hasn't been updated in a long time. As a result, the owners of those devices can't enjoy the latest features or optimizations...
::::'''Thea:''' Locals may experience issues such as lagging or overheating on their phones, but it's simply because they don't know how to upgrade the system...
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} So, you're planning to make a fortune out of this?
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031257-->
:::::'''Thea:''' Hey, that's hardly the case at all! I swear I was telling you the truth... And to be honest, even a simple system upgrade can be an exclusive gimmick on a remote planet like this.
:::::'''Thea:''' Just please don't tell anyone... Director Topaz threw the book at those troublemakers in the Underworld... I'm just a phone tinkerer who hasn't done anything to put the residents in harm's way.
:::::'''Thea:''' ...How about you take this thing for now? The fewer complications the better. Just treat this as the beginning of a new friendship...
