:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I have some questions about the IPC...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501031203_68-->
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} What do you make of Topaz?
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031266-->
:::::'''Thea:''' Director Topaz? Well, I'm just a low-level employee, and I don't really have a chance to talk with her.
:::::'''Thea:''' But according to everyone, she's sociable, loves her work, and more importantly, has a kind heart.
:::::'''Thea:''' I think she's probably the least terrible among all the eleven directors in my department.
:::::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501031203_68-->
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501031203_68-->
::::;(<!--Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString)-->)
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} Are there many planets indebted to IPC?
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031270-->
::::::'''Thea:''' I can't say for sure, as I don't have access to certain statistics.
::::::'''Thea:''' However, we do have a Marketing Development Department that focuses on bringing new planets into the galactic market.
::::::'''Thea:''' Sometimes, those planets will borrow startup funds from us, dreaming of becoming major players in the galaxy in an Amber Era or two.
::::::'''Thea:''' However, these planets bite off more than they can chew, and they often end up becoming targets for my department.
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} How much do you get paid?
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031275-->
::::::'''Thea:''' Hey, you see... it's a trade secret.
::::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Just spill the beans!
::::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What's so secretive about it?
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031278-->
::::::'''Thea:''' I'm sorry, but I just can't spill the beans on that one!
